      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 00:25:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>创纪录的债务成本意味着气候支出可能会将各国推向破产边缘</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/record-debt-costs-mean-climate-spending-could-push-nations-brink-insolvency-2024-04-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波士顿大学牵头发布的一份报告显示，今年新兴国家将支付创纪录的 4000 亿美元来偿还外债，近 40 个国家在未来五年内无法在不冒违约风险的情况下花费气候适应和可持续发展所需的资金。国际货币基金组织/世界银行春季会议前夕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/record-debt-costs-mean-climate-spending-could-push-nations-brink-insolvency-2024-04-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 00:03:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东冲突席卷市场，亚洲股市下滑，黄金坚挺</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，亚洲股市下跌，金价上涨，因伊朗对以色列的报复性袭击引发了对更广泛地区冲突的担忧，令交易员紧张不安，风险情绪受到打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 23:58:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
